data.description: $20K Price Improvement!!! QUALIFIES FOR VA LOAN ASSUMPTION AT UNDER 3% INTEREST FOR VETERANS!!!! Sellers requested no showing until after the Christmas Holiday. Welcome to your dream home in Thompson River Ranch, Northern Colorado. This 3-story single-family residence offers stunning views of the Rockies from your west facing bedroom windows. Largest lot on the street! Enjoy daily vistas of the Rocky Mountains in all their colorful glory, setting the scene for a serene and inspiring lifestyle. The main floor features an open layout with a gorgeous kitchen island, ample room for a kitchen table and direct flow to the living room area as well as a formal dining room. Upstairs features an office for remote work or creative pursuits, ensuring a well-balanced living space as well as 4 bedrooms, upstairs laundry for ease of cleaning, and a spacious primary bedroom with en-suite bathroom and walk-in closet for your ultimate comfort. All four bedrooms are generously sized. On the third floor is a versatile flex space for a game room, home theater, gym, or an additional office area. Say goodbye to parking hassles with ample room for three vehicles in the garage and an additional three vehicle off-street parking. Your private oasis for outdoor activities, gardening, and relaxation in the hot tub await. This property is located in a metro district and has HOA covenants, however there are no monthly or annual fees. For verification and more information, please visit the link provided in the listing. Covenants apply only to maintain community standards and protect your investment. Thompson River Ranch offers easy access to shopping, dining, outdoor adventures, and more. This property combines luxury, comfort, and convenience in a desirable Northern Colorado community. Don't miss out-schedule a showing today and make this your forever home.Qualifies for VA Loan Assumption under 3% interest for Veterans, FHA, Conventional Financing. NO showings until after the Christmas Holiday.
